ca.uwo.csd.cs2212.group5

Class MarsCurrent

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.uwo.csd.cs2212.group5.MarsCurrent

  • public class MarsCurrent
extends java.lang.Object
    Used as a datatype object that stores various parameters that describe the current weather on Mars. Getter and setter methods are provided for all parameters, in addition to a constructor.
    Author:
    CS2212 Team 5
